Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九十八  九十九
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ninety-eight, 99
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:33.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(536,298)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.87,0:01:44.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能找到办法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:44.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only I could find a way
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.54,0:01:47.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把海绵宝宝给甩掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:47.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get SpongeBob out of my hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:47.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(860,920)}让海绵宝宝别碰我头发
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚有说话吗  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you say something, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.38,0:01:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.79,0:01:55.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我表现比昨天好多了吗  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:55.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did way better than yesterday, didn't I, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yesterday
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.18,0:02:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外国驾校交换生计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Foreign Student Driver Exchange Program"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交换生计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exchange program?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.06,0:02:14.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正是摆脱海绵宝宝的大好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:14.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my chance to be rid of SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.53,0:02:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚说什么  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是很欣赏这大好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just admiring this amazing opportunity
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the opportunity?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.49,0:02:25.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾校交换生计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:25.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A student driver exchange program
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要用学生来交换什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you exchange the student for?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.46,0:02:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个学生会从一个遥远的神奇国度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A student from a faraway magical country
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫做可乐那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,called Klopnod
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:35.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(624,246)}可乐那
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来这里学习我们的驾驶方式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,comes here to learn our way of driving
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神奇国度可乐那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magical country of Klopnod?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且可神了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要找个同学派过去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just have to find a student to send there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要热爱乐趣的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone that loves fun
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我热爱乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love fun
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要追求冒险的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A student that lives for adventure
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我追求冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I live for adventure
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.27,0:02:55.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还是最渴望学开船的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A student that wants to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how to drive more than anything
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.69,0:02:58.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最渴望学的就是开船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:58.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to learn how to drive more than anything
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是莫大的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's such a big honor
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是不知道要派谁过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just don't know who to send
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.20,0:03:03.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:03.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pick me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.66,0:03:03.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:03.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.99,0:03:04.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要乐趣  冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:04.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want fun, adventure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要学习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and learning
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托选我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please pick me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.25,0:03:11.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果那对你意义这么重大  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:11.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it means that much to you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也等不及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neither can I
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的介绍信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your introduction letter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728,254)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(624,542)}裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1274,194)}酷乐湖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:32.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(862,832)}石头滩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(990,988)}无人区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1028,956)}可乐那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,486)}欢迎来到\N可乐那
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的介绍信沾满了泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got mud all over my introduction letter
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定就是交换生海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be exchange student SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  是的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大多数同学都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Most student not know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可乐那族泥巴欢迎仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Klopnodian Mud greeting
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你准备好学开船了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ready for to learn how to drive?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,768)}海绵宝宝\N学员档案
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定就是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be my
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交换生胡椒子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,exchange student, Peppercorn
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只会可乐那语
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You only speak Klopnodian
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.93,0:04:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望这语言障碍不会影响我的教学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope this language barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,doesn't impact my teaching
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好见你的同学们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for meeting your fellow students?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我随时都准备好要见其他驾驶爱好者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm always ready to meet other driving enthusiasts
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.28,0:05:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Students
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们  这位是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone, this SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是裤头村来的外国交换生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is foreign exchange student from Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  教练老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mr. Driving Instructor, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些貌似都是家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but these look like farm animals
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.00,0:05:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No offense
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.21,0:05:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可乐那只允许动物驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In Klopnod, only animals allowed to drive
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样大家才会比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's safer for everyone that way
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好迷人的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a fascinating culture
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,聊够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough making talk
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get learning
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,击掌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,High five
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正式开始驾驶之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Before we getting to driving
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.82,0:05:50.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先回顾一下交通规则
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:50.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we go over rules of road
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,规则1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rule 1:
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.83,0:05:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一次上路如果看见自己的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you are seeing your shadow when you first enter road
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就回船库两周
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,go back to garage for two weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,规则2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rule 2:
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母永远优先通行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish always have right of way
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每月奇数天除外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,except on odd days of the month
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师从来没教过我这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff never taught me any of this stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  胡椒子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, Peppercorn
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是时候要上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to get behind the wheel
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我来评测你的驾驶技能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can assess your driving skills
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是比海绵宝宝强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still better than SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来学习第一课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's start with lesson one, shall we?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先检查后视镜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, check your mirrors
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天一定会很难熬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be a long day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:40.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(688,264)}出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1360,376)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在慢下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now slow down
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,检查盲区  打转向信号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check your blind spot, use your turn signal
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.56,0:06:58.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从人行道汇入主路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:58.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and merge from the walkway into the street
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.19,0:07:05.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:05.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡椒子  你开得完美无瑕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peppercorn, your driving is flawless
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你完全可以上高速了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you're ready for freeway driving
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以上就是所有规则
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that is all of rules
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来开船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now for to make with the driving
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发动机在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the engine?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们轮流当发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Students take turns being engine
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep calm, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.18,0:07:38.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在老家通常都是开船这步搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:38.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Driving is the part you usually mess up back home
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  没看见我的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, no sign of my shadow
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.32,0:07:54.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:54.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've failed again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我永远也学不会开船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never learn how to drive
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You crazy?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.03,0:08:32.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我见过最厉害的司机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:32.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You greatest driver I ever see
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,R-really?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边所有人开船都像我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone here drives like me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你应得的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've earned this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一颗芜菁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A turnip
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.06,0:09:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't eat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看背面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Read other side
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可乐那官方驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Official Klopnod Driving License
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,持照人  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,issued to SpongeBob SquarePants"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now go
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡椒子  我怀着无比的自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peppercorn, with great pride
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.26,0:09:39.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为你颁发裤头村驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:39.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I present you with a Bikini Bottom Driver's License
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真为你自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud of you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你得回可乐那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you have to go back to Klopnod
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but remember
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在裤头村永远有个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you always have a friend in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的尖子生就这么走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There goes the best student
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.25,0:10:07.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能教她是我莫大的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:07.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've ever had the honor to teach
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡椒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peppercorn?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师好  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mrs. Puff, I'm back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这么快就被踢出驾校了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They kick you out of driving school already?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I graduated
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.89,0:10:24.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可乐那驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:24.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Klopnodian Driving License?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道你过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You passed?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该只是需要换个环境吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess I just needed a change of scenery
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我来给你展示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to show you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我新学到的可乐那持照驾驶技能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my new Klopnodian licensed driving skills?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.40,0:10:37.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得不说  我很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:37.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to say, I am curious
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,两分钟后
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.91,0:10:46.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得我这可乐那族驾驶技能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:46.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think of my Klopnodian driving skills?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.00,0:10:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就跟裤头村不适配
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't translate to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1480,230)}前方火山峡谷
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  就快冲向火山峡谷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, we're headed for Volcano Gorge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打方向盘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn the wheel
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.92,0:10:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在打了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm turning
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.31,0:11:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, look
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是胡椒子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peppercorn
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're saved
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.21,0:11:36.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我还没准备好在裤头村开船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm not ready for driving
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Bikini Bottom just yet
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  胡椒子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, Peppercorn
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你比我更配得上这个驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you deserve this license more than I do
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.47,0:11:46.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我明天一大早就要来上课见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll be seeing you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bright and early for class tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.06,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFC1&}恐堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(750,408)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(768,700)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:57.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(636,484)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(800,700)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.41,0:12:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人现在该来安稳睡个懒觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for Master to sleep tight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and bite the bedbugs good night
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带来了你最爱的睡前茶点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought your favorite bedtime tea
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,血橙汁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blood Orange
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不加橙汁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold the Orange
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Woe is me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fired?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I beg your forgiveness
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来这都是我应得的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose I deserve this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,几小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  史赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Slappy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在里面干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what're you doing in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着收垃圾的过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waiting for the waste man
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.58,0:13:41.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妥善处理我凋零又毫无价值的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:41.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to properly dispose of my withering, worthless soul
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才没凋零呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not withering
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有主人  我迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without a master, I am lost
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要打磨谁的棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whose coffin do I polish?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要削尖谁的尖牙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whose fangs do I sharpen?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.35,0:14:00.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要伺候别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:00.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to serve somebody
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任何人都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anybody
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别磨蹭了  回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit your lollygagging and get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人又不会自己服务自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those customers won't serve themselves
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is a lotta customers
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来今天得找帮手了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like we could use some help today, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.83,0:14:18.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:18.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我乐意为你效劳  主人老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to be at your service, Mister Master
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.22,0:14:29.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我没钱再另外雇佣劳力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:29.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't afford to pay another hand
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的旧主人付我昆虫当报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My old master paid me in insects
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.27,0:14:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灭虫人员兼服务生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An exterminator and a server?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直是买一送一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a two-for-one deal
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被录用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're hired
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我帮你保管外套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to take your coat?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.16,0:14:55.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:55.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是我谢谢你  好先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thank you, good sir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.54,0:15:00.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是蟹堡王里值得给小费的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:00.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that's the tip-worthy service this place needs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep it up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮你保管外套吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I take your coat?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我没穿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm not wearing a--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用餐愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your meal
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.39,0:15:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这家伙是蟹老板雇过最可怕的怪人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy is the creepiest weirdo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs has ever hired
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I stand corrected
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  弗雷迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Mr. Freddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的新鲜食物等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your fresh food awaits you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh my
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,leg
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吓跑客人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scaring away the customers?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板一定会爱上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is gonna love this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.72,0:15:56.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史赖皮  目前为止干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:56.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Slappy, great work so far
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人们都很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The customers love ya
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大多是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mostly
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.52,0:16:02.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但还是别给客人吃太不寻常的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:02.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But let's not feed the customers anything too unusual
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像是客人自己的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like their own leg
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good point
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胳膊大概会更多汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arms can be so much juicer
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如给客人端上他们点的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about serving our customers what they ordered
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这点子真新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a novel idea
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴能达成共识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad we're on the same page
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, madame
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得不说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must say
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.59,0:16:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的燕尾服真是领班级的美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your tuxedo is maître-d'-lightful
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我被埋葬时穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the suit I was buried in
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh my
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像你这样高雅的女士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sophisticated lady like yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该坐在全餐厅最好的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,deserves the best seat in the house
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put me down
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.57,0:17:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来先吃个史赖皮开胃蟹黄堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:17:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I start you off with a Slappy-tizing Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托就要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, I insist
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还帮你嚼过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll even chew it for you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(478,536)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.18,0:17:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冒犯到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am offended
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这位领头服务生接下来要服务谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, as head waiter, who can I help next?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.86,0:17:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面干嘛在尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's with all the screaming out here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史赖皮先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slappy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我蟹堡王的老主顾都吓跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're creepin' away all me loyal Krustomers
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  史赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Slappy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板对犯错还是很宽容的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is very tolerant of mistakes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是我应得的  主人老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I deserve this, Mister Master
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我无法再接受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can no longer accept
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.92,0:17:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为我糟糕的服务支付的丰厚报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your generous payment for my terrible service
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is a shame though
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我邀请了很多朋友来这用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've invited lots of friends to eat here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由我为他们服务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I could serve them
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很多朋友是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lots of friends, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.40,0:18:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你这么多朋友什么时候要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So when would these "lots of friends" be comin' aboard?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天黑之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After dark
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被录用回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're unfired
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.63,0:18:34.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暂时是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:34.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最好动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had better hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整修一下这里  迎接他们到来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and fix this place up for them
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.11,0:18:57.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份科学怪堡  给科学怪鱼主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:57.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Franken-patty for Master Frankenfish
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能麻烦你一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you do the honors?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's alive
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃的堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patty good
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一根备用骨头  给狼人先
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A spare for Mister Were
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wolf
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.06,0:19:30.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用骨愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:30.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bone appétit
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给隐形鱼的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And for The Invisible Fish
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐形菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an invisible dish
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.90,0:19:38.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:38.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不加隐形蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold the invisible mayo
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能重做了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I have to start over
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monsters
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史赖皮小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slappy-lad
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要让我发大财了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're making me rich
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep it up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高兴点  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物钱还是钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monster money is still money
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good news, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们所有丑八怪  还有你们的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you hideous beasts, and your money
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.57,0:20:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随时都欢迎光临蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are welcome at the Krusty Krab anytime
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的旧主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My old master?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你样子不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't look too good
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that you say, Master?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一走  就没人帮你理头发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without me, you have nobody to cut your hair
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.80,0:20:48.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,削尖尖牙  让你保持黑白配色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:48.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sharpen your fangs, or keep you in black and white?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.10,0:20:53.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:53.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,need me?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.11,0:21:00.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好久都想听你嘶嘶地说出这些话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:21:00.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,, how long I've wanted to hear you hiss those words
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.82,0:21:08.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:08.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你  主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you, Mast--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续工作  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to work boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然了  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.92,0:21:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿意回来做你的小奴才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would love to come back and be your lowly minion
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slappy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别丢下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.81,0:21:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该做我的小奴才才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to be my lowly minion
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生气的村民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Angry villagers?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我们很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are angry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但也还很饿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we're also hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.16,0:21:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.87,0:21:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又气又饿的村民吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hangry villagers, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.91,0:21:54.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:54.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even better
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边请  无法无天的暴民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right this way, unruly mob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就给大家凑点吃的来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll scare up some food for ya
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.04,0:22:03.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡最能团结大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:02.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing brings everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.92,0:22:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甚至能团结生气的村民和他们的宿敌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even angry villagers and their mortal enemies
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.30,0:22:08.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:08.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,monsters
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.56,0:22:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些是怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are those monsters?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.43,0:22:17.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住它们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:17.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get them
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.19,0:22:27.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:27.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh well
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是赚到了怪物的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still have the monster money
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.99,0:22:36.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来怪物的钱是虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:36.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monster money is bugs
